  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You shake your body to a phantom beat as chakra shrouds you, transforming you into a lively monkey with surprising agility. While concentrating on this jutsu, you are unable to cast jutsu or make weapon attacks. Additionally, you gain the following benefits;</p><ul><li>You count as one size smaller and gain a +2 bonus to your AC.</li><li>Your movement speed increased by 10 feet. Additionally, you gain a climbing equal to your movement speed.</li><li><p>As an action you may perform a straight-line dash through your enemies, having them make a dexterity saving throw as you shoot straight towards them dealing 2d8 bludgeoning damage on a failure.</p></li></ul><p><strong>At Higher Ranks:</strong> For each rank you cast this jutsu above D-Rank, increase the chakra cost by 3, increase the damage by 1d8, and the range by 10 feet. If cast at B-rank or higher, creatures make the save at disadvantage.</p>",
